eventDecorators.name: OwnershipTransferred
eventDecorators.description: An event emitted when a vault is liquidated.

eventDecorators.name: presaleRegistered
eventDecorators.description: An event emitted when a vault is liquidated.

functionDecorators.name: owner
functionDecorators.description: Returns the address of the current owner.

functionDecorators.name: presaleAtIndex
functionDecorators.description: gets a presale at a specific index. Although using Enumerable Set, since presales are only added and not removed, indexes will never change.

returnDecorators.description: the address of the Presale contract at index.

functionDecorators.name: presaleGeneratorAtIndex
functionDecorators.description: Gets the address of a registered PresaleGenerator at specified index.

functionDecorators.name: presaleIsRegistered
functionDecorators.description: returns true if the presale address was generated by the Octofi presale platform.

functionDecorators.name: presalesLength
functionDecorators.description: The length of all presales on the platform.

functionDecorators.name: registerPresale
functionDecorators.description: called by a registered PresaleGenerator upon Presale creation.

functionDecorators.name: renounceOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

functionDecorators.name: transferOwnership
functionDecorators.description: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
